### PetClinic Owners API - Sample Requests
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5276

### Get API Info
GET {{baseUrl}}/

### Create Owner
POST {{baseUrl}}/owners
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Doe",
  "address": "123 Main Street",
  "city": "Springfield",
  "telephone": "555-1234"
}

### Create Another Owner
POST {{baseUrl}}/owners
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Jane",
  "lastName": "Smith",
  "address": "456 Oak Avenue",
  "city": "Riverside",
  "telephone": "555-5678"
}

### Get Owner by ID (replace {id} with actual owner ID from create response)
GET {{baseUrl}}/owners/{id}

### Search Owners (no query - returns all)
GET {{baseUrl}}/owners

### Search Owners by query
GET {{baseUrl}}/owners?query=Doe

### Search Owners by telephone
GET {{baseUrl}}/owners?query=555-1234

### Update Owner (replace {id} with actual owner ID)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/owners/{id}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Doe",
  "address": "789 Updated Street",
  "city": "Springfield",
  "telephone": "555-9999"
}
